Properties.Description:
An event that affects two parties within a relationship each performing a specified role.
 
Ex:

PARTY 1 = Kevin Bryson
ROLE 1 = Employee
PARTY 2 = Davis Corp.
ROLE 2 = Employer
PARTY RELATIONSHIP TYPE = Employment
EVENT TYPE = Employment Layoff

PARTY 1 = Kevin Bryson
ROLE 1 = Customer
PARTY 2 = Mary Bryson
ROLE 2 = Customer
PARTY RELATIONSHIP TYPE = Marriage
EVENT TYPE = Birth of Child
PARTY RELATIONSHIP NOTE = Kevin Bryson and Mary Bryson who are customers recorded the birth of a child on the indicated date
